@startuml
autonumber
actor "CRM Collaborator" as User
participant ":System" as System

activate User
User -> System : Starts "Add/Remove Video of Proposal"
activate System
System --> User : Shows list of safe proposals and asks to select one
deactivate System

User -> System : Selects a proposal
activate System
System --> User : Asks to add or remove the video
deactivate System

alt Add Video
    User -> System : Chooses to add a video
    activate System
    System --> User : Prompts for the video link
    deactivate System

    User -> System : Enters the video link
    activate System
    System --> User : Confirms that the video was added successfully
    deactivate System
else Remove Video
    User -> System : Chooses to remove the video
    activate System
    System --> User : Confirms that the video was removed successfully
    deactivate System
end

deactivate User
@enduml
